00:06:35.800 --> 00:06:37.120
magbigay ng ilang payo?

00:06:40.800 --> 00:06:42.640
Tinatanggihan pa rin bang maging tapat?

00:06:53.280 --> 00:06:55.160
Ito ba ang iyong tunay na layunin

00:06:55.160 --> 00:06:56.320
